      <scopecontent id="aspace_scope">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains correspondence written by Ruth "Babs" Bernstein to her parents and sister "Mar". A dedicated correspondent, the collection contains daily and weekly letters from the entirety of her first year through her junior year at Smith College. The collection also contains a few letters received during her time at Smith College as well as a number of pamphlets, flyers, and class notes from 1945 - 1949.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_scope-org">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>This collection is organized into two series:</p>    
         <list type="ordered">
            <item>Correspondence Sent</item>
            <item>Correspondence Received</item>
         </list>
      </arrangement>
